					"type": 23,
					"value": "Go to Iron Throne\r\nDebug add the stones (example, oe glo_emperorprelude_gortash)\r\nDrop one or more stones\r\nLeave Iron Throne\r\ngoto 35 7 -142\r\nGo to the beach"
